                <p>A new species of <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Rugilus</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Leach, <tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Rugilus</tp:taxon-name-part> (<tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="subgenus">Rugilus</tp:taxon-name-part>) <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">huanghaoi</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name> <bold>sp. n.</bold> from Qinling, Shaanxi Province, China, is described and illustrated. Additional records of seven species from Qinling are reported.</p>
